result.name: 新大光燈

reviews.text: A small local eatery famous for wanton noodles with a humble history in Hung Hom, and the noodles is one of the best in the region, and pricing is fair.  Expect no fancy deco but clean and cool.
Very great traditional Cantonese snacks you could try here. Execllent Wonton noodle.
I love their beef soup and service
Their wonton noodle is very very tasty. U must try it.
Nice food with very reasonable price

result.name: 新大光燈

reviews.text: 偶然路過，入去進食。食品味道不錯啊！ 可惜地點不太就腳。
豬潤同雲吞麵都好食
食物有水準，粥底绵滑，炸凌魚球外趣内軟，好食！
味道幾好，但味精也好多
各樣麵食可以 價錢則略徧高
